---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="GM Information - OZ ORC Adelaide | Resources for Game Masters"
  description="Essential information for Game Masters running games at OZ ORC. Find resources, safety tools, and what to bring to Adelaide's premier OSR gaming convention."
>
  <section class="bg-base-200 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">GM INFORMATION</h1>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Resources and guidelines for Game Masters at OZ ORC
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-sm">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">Support & Resources</h2>

            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Safety Tools</h3>
              <p class="mb-4">
                In a convention environment, GMs will often be running games for strangers with varied backgrounds and experiences. If you're interested in learning about tools to help facilitate games in these situations, here are some excellent resources:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-primary">→</span>
                  <a
                    href="/code-of-conduct"
                    class="link link-primary"
                  >
                    OZ ORC Code of Conduct
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-primary">→</span>
                  <a
                    href="https://ttrpgsafetytoolkit.com"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="link link-primary"
                  >
                    TTRPG Safety Toolkit
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-primary">→</span>
                  <a
                    href="https://slyflourish.com/safety_tools.html"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="link link-primary"
                  >
                    Sly Flourish's Guide to Safety Tools
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-primary">→</span>
                  <a
                    href="https://montecookgames.com/consent-in-gaming/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="link link-primary"
                  >
                    Monte Cook Games: Consent in Gaming
                  </a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Contact</h3>
              <p>
                If you have any questions or need assistance, please reach out to the organizers at{' '}
                <a href="mailto:admin@ozorc.com" class="link link-primary">
                  admin@ozorc.com
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <a
            href="/gm-submission"
            class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
          >
            Submit Your Game
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
